## Project management

- Creation
  - `npx create-expo-app@latest`
- Start development server
  - `npx expo start --dev-client`

## Project structure

- `package.json`
  - Package and version control
  - App styling
    - Icon
    - Name
    - Splash screen
- `tsx`
  - `index.tsx`
    - Default page
  - `_layout.tsx`
    - `<Stack>`
    - `<Tabs>`
    - Optional overwrite in page tsx files
  - `not-found.tsx`
  - `tsconfig.json`
    - Control included tsx/jsx files

